{"tid":1660110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家母打算星期日第一次去遊行，手足可唔可以鼓勵下佢？","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T12:16:49.000Z","uid":114252,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"779c506001379e90756d1c8933df9433169cc04e","tid":1660110,"uid":114252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"平時會陪屋企一齊睇港台d節目，尤其鏗鏘集<br />\n家母七月開始由中立慢慢變淺黃到依家深黃<br />\n見到火魔法都唔割接受到<br />\n<br />\n每次屋企睇live，佢都睇到好心痛<br />\n奈何身體唔好，一直都無試過遊行，最多都係去集會同人鍊活動，平時戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n佢見到有手足一齊戴口罩，有互望既話會比個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日佢主動話星期日佢都想去，真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我知道佢情緒依幾個月都屈住屈住，同埋知道d狗會亂咬人，會擔心安全。<br />\n各位手足可唔可以比d鼓勵家母？<br />\n希望會令佢情緒會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\np.s.小小建議， 每個手足帶多個人，人數就已經多一倍。除左文宣，可以試下開口問身邊既人會唔會去。<br />\n<br />\n行動：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qZAbaX9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZAbaX9.jpg&h=df58a7ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziystKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziystKR.jpg&h=8ec5cea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bm0RVuo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBm0RVuo.jpg&h=8fb8adc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57a979414a17bb7d64b590ccff2fb07b69768ef4","tid":1660110,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"f26621dc7b66debd809062d9861364da66d740ae","tid":1660110,"uid":183834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4A4n2ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4A4n2ab.jpg&h=2782e738&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"672d2bceaaede68ccc9f7703d50aa9bd34538418","tid":1660110,"uid":114252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:24:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b929ee1f3062959dc463d8606f2da82c3ffe572","tid":1660110,"uid":114252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e58d9250b641352c101f9c7b145ca56cbac6955","tid":1660110,"uid":168717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"有黃色屋企人真係好"},{"pid":"b56c51ad265953f782ec97b75b6e98eb5a26dbd6","tid":1660110,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"推呀 大家叫埋身邊人一齊出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢行 慢慢行 行多d活動多d身體健康d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ec29dc7ba95191bfd0539572ff13645ddc6937","tid":1660110,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"加油呀 伯母"},{"pid":"249498b611ef0a6663c6dfa0beadd20300cad569","tid":1660110,"uid":126100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"早D去唔洗逼，又易行D<br />\n<br />\n伯母加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f957e1982aa162fd1601c0524d6609288ac8859","tid":1660110,"uid":299134,"li